# AppArmor local override for msmtp
# Copy to /etc/apparmor.d/local/usr.bin.msmtp
#
# Grants msmtp exactly what The Watcher needs and nothing else:
#   - Read any file under /etc/msmtp/ (the logwatcher msmtp config)
#   - Write to logwatcher's log directory
#
# After copying, reload the profile:
#   sudo apparmor_parser -r /etc/apparmor.d/usr.bin.msmtp

/etc/msmtp/* r,
/var/lib/logwatcher/*.log wk,
